{"tid":906030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"54歲休班警 涉非禮16歲少女被捕","createTime":"2018-11-17T15:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T16:18:29.000Z","uid":5195,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8c37eec1e2d4b9e2002d1eff61f10fc2373a2887","tid":906030,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:28:49.000Z","msg":"休班警涉非禮16歲少女被捕<br />\n17.11.2018 21:52<br />\n一名休班警員涉嫌非禮少女被捕。事發在昨日早上，54歲休班男警員在港鐵荔景站月台，涉嫌非禮一名16歲少女，警方接報到場將他拘捕，他已獲准保釋候查，十二月中旬要向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，非常重視警員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，都絕不容忍和姑息，定必會嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1042332&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1042332%26csid%3D261_341&d=Ao7t8yvT3hs8ulZu38hyotU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f6765d13\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1042332&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"98eadcccaffe9b75ce3ec68819529bbbef12d4b3","tid":906030,"uid":73613,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b257dbf7bb3f4c0bb27db85c15cd0386531726b7","tid":906030,"uid":45740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fb714ddb6bb52052fd5b3b4add92a83ac9cdd9","tid":906030,"uid":36238,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:33:58.000Z","msg":"警方指，非常重視警員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，都絕不容忍和姑息，定必會嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"c95873eb24c70601ab20e84c4fdb3d2b1337b6fb","tid":906030,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"呢個#me too女受害人 我就選擇相信"},{"pid":"a6beea4cb5ca8c70cc70d80cfc3703bdc5491311","tid":906030,"uid":78141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"就退休就忍下手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.